WEBVTT

41:53.790 --> 41:56.970 line:80%
The matrilocal husband must change
his surname according to tradition.

41:56.970 --> 41:57.610 line:80%
No need.

41:58.260 --> 42:00.420 line:80%
My husband doesn't need to
change his surname.

42:00.420 --> 42:01.350 line:80%
He'll keep the name Yan Zheng.
